          <div class="col-3">
        
  
  


<div class="top-story">
  <a href="/extremism-watch/rising-ashes-womans-campaign-rescue-mosuls-books" title="Rising From the Ashes: A Womanâs Campaign to Rescue Mosulâs Books">
          
            <div><div>
  
  
            <div>    <img srcset="https://im-media.voltron.voanews.com/Drupal/01live-166/styles/817x459/s3/2019-11/ashes.jpg?itok=4Gcb_Gpr 1x" src="https://im-media.voltron.voanews.com/Drupal/01live-166/styles/485x273/s3/2019-11/ashes.jpg?itok=Snt9eny7" alt="FILE -- Tahany Saleh walks through a pile of debris at the gate of Mosul Universityâs Central Library as she works with her volunteer team to rescue books in the burned building, Mosul, Iraq, May 2017.  " />


</div>
      
</div>
</div>
      
      </a>
  <div class="top-story__content">
          <a href="/extremism-watch" class="eyebrow top-story__eyebrow">Extremism Watch</a>
        <h3 class="top-story__title">
      <a class="top-story__title-link" href="/extremism-watch/rising-ashes-womans-campaign-rescue-mosuls-books"><span>Rising From the Ashes: A Womanâs Campaign to Rescue Mosulâs Books</span>
</a>
    </h3>
      </div>
</div>

      </div>
